Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy shit. To think that Ginji's gone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A 7 Man dora
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The dora have been flowing to Soga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Soga in this, the 4th hand
