Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Declaring Riichi on a Dora Haitei draw
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a possibility of a Dora pair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's Mangan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I've got 3 of the Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,means there's but one in his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dora single tile wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And since he's on a Dora wait, if he draws it himself his hand reaches Haneman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But as I've collected 3 Dora during play
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Soga's wait has vanished
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just unlucky I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wait is already dead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's accumulated 3 Dora, hasn't he
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, Akagi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gift from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The 4th Dora tile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You did that, didn't you Soga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is something to see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm deliberately provoking Akagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's not the kind to back down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just see if he'll try to use that Dora I gave him to win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid's at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi's hand, with an Ippatsu Tsumo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and 4 Dora, it's a Haneman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he wins, he'll drop the kid's points to 1,000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll let the win pass
