Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to win when you can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you calling tiles...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But winning's the thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi...
