Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:18:00.55,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(815.111,122)}West Team\NHarada: {\c&H0000FF&}7000 {\c&HFFFFFF&}Mitsui: 17000\NSoga: 25000 Akutsu: 11000
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:18:00.55,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1111.555,532.222)}Game 8\NSouth Hand 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jyunchan, SanSyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With dealer bonus it's 12,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi's declared Riichi when not in tenpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and that Illegal Kan has begun to tilt the game flow to the East team
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:36.28,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278.667,122)}East Team\NTen: 12000{\c&HFFFFFF&} Hiroyuki: 3000\NAkagi: 16000
