Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:36.28,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1111.555,532.222)}Game 9\NEast Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting cocky
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Going for a toitoi or honiisou hand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,by putting together East and West triplets
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,he's got a Mangan hand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this Chitoitsu hand doesn't carry any Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't even amount to a Mangan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever contest I enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't afraid what some pipsqueak with only 3000 points left plays
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he's going down
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tanyao or Sansyoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover with the remaining 5 pin Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He carries Three Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's gathered up a Toitoi it's a baiman hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaay. With this tile I've got a Tanyao
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mangan without even declaring Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This hand is just between me and Akagi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The brat's also in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going for a single suit hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to die that badly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I'll knock him out of the game
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Harada looks like he's holding a Pinzu (dots) Honisou hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and they expect him to discard a 5 pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well THAT'S a style of play I've never thought of before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I discard the 3 Sou I'll take the hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but that previous 5 Pin discard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering the kid's Honiisou the 3 Sou is extremely dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Harada could be in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll choose to deal into his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll discard a 2 Pin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point I've got to do what I've got to do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Head Bump
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:23.08,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,{\pos(639.111,609.555)}Head Bump or Atamahane(頭跳ね): In the case of two Ron calls, awarding the Ron to the player closest to the discarder, in wind order. This is in contrast to the Double Ron (or Triple Ron) rule which allows multiple point payouts on simultaneous Ron calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,East West Toitoi 3 Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A Haneman win
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:32.68,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Even though Hiroyuki had 4 Dora he avoided declaring Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:36.58,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Aiming instead to win via a much more effective single tile wait
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:40.61,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Thus Hiroyuki chose a 2 Pin wait
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:45.51,Default - top,,0,0,0,,As Hiroyuki  SEEMED to have a sou Honiisou, it wasn't a likely wait
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:52.98,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Then, discarding one of his Dora...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.98,0:23:54.98,Default - top,,0,0,0,,a direct hit here would mean instant death
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:56.88,Default - top,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:58.88,Default - top,,0,0,0,,what if it passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:01.61,Default - top,,0,0,0,,it becomes the ULTIMATE camouflage
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid's been cautious up to now
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.91,0:24:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he now play putting his life on the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is in Akagi's hand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.15,0:24:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That hand there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is a bluff
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:27.48,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Akagi wasn't aiming for a win himself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.25,0:24:30.25,Default - top,,0,0,0,,but rather to protect the kid
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.25,0:24:32.25,Default - top,,0,0,0,,He shielded him
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.25,0:24:34.98,Default - top,,0,0,0,,and that's emboldened the kid
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.98,0:24:36.98,Default - top,,0,0,0,,It's been transmitted
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.95,0:24:41.08,Default - top,,0,0,0,,The ultimate sensibility of an Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:43.08,Default - top,,0,0,0,,His spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.91,0:24:46.78,Default - top,,0,0,0,,This ain't good
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.55,0:24:53.55,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.01,0:24:57.51,Default - top,,0,0,0,,HE'S TRANSFORMED
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.05,0:25:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU DICK!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.05,0:25:08.41,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.41,0:25:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already decided what we have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.28,0:25:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is battle of base instinct
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.28,0:25:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon yourself entirely to it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.75,0:25:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I WON'T ACCEPT THIS KIND OF MAHJONG!
